  <source>Nagoya University</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We investigated whether treatment of central sleep apnea-hypopnea with bilevel positive
      airway pressure (BiPAP) in patients with idiopathic dilated cardiomyopathy (IDCM) would
      improve LV function.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
